fields.name: GREEN CUP
fields.description:
This ceramic green cup is the perfect addition to your dinner set. 
Its elegant design and natural shades of green will give your table
a sophisticated look. Made from high quality ceramic, this plate is
strong and durable, making it the perfect choice for everyday use. 
Thanks to its matte surface, it not only looks stylish,
but is also pleasant to the touch.
